Dialogs.Dialog: (I know！ I should invite her to travel to Nikko/ Kinugawa...)
I won a travel prize again.
Amazing！ Is it a travel to Atami？
An adult trip to Nikko/ Kinugawa hot springs, one night and two days！！
Well, we're still not "adults", but it sounds a little interesting, right？
No, that's not it！ It's just...
Hmm... It's okay. I have decided.
Can we go？ It's a school trip just for two people.
But, isn't it something that makes you feel uncomfortable？
Yes, I want to go on a school trip. Yes... it looks fun！
By the way... is it really okay？ You know... with your father.
I'll be fine？ Because he already knows I went to Atami with you.
I see. No... wait a minute.
I don't like to lie, so I asked Mama to help me explain it properly. Then "he felt relief".
Yes, something like "If you look at Manaka, you know that it didn't happen."
It's something strange... Well, you're right.
He said "He looks like a good young man, which is rare nowadays."
I see, I see... Your father is surprisingly understanding！
Also, he said "If he's about to do something strange, call me. No matter where you are, I'll rush right away."
Hehe！ And then？ When will we do it？
(Umm, I should set a date to go...)
Then, from ▲月▲▲日▲, a one-night, two-day school trip！ Nothing strange will happen！
I don't think it's weird to share a kiss every now and then...
(I did it！！ Me and ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s school trip together！)
(I know！ I should invite her to Nikko/ Kinuguwa again...)
Actually, I won it again！ Our adult Nikko/ Kinugawa hot spring's school trip！
Hey, hey... But, isn't this overdoing it？
Huh？ Oh, well, you're might be right...
Hmm... I'm happy either way. I want to go on a school trip together.
Alright！ We will go enjoy ourselves once more...
Umm, we should set our date day...
Then, from ▲月▲▲日▲, it's a one-night, two-day school trip！
Yes！ It's a school trip！ Hehe！
(Yay！！ Me and ▲高嶺＊＊▲ will have another school trip alone！)
I'm sorry for suddenly calling you. Would you like to go shopping for the trip now？
For the trip？ Do you need something？
It's because it's a school trip, right？ I think we need various things.
I wonder about that... Well, it's okay.
Okay. Well then, I'll be waiting.
So, you know what you'll buy？？
I made an inventory list, so yes.
Oh, it's really full. Lemme see, uh... sickness meds, wet tissues, trekking shoes, thick socks... playing cards？
It's because we're on a school trip, right？ Don't you want to use play with it at night？
I see, that might be good！
(Wait... We're going to Kinugawa hot springs, so there may be a family bath again...)
Are you okay with buying a swimsuit, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Well, you know, maybe there is a family bath like in Atami？
Now then, is this all of the shopping list？
Yes, that's all. Make sure to pack early, okay？ If you do it in the morning, you may forget something.
Don't you sound like a sensei, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Hehe！ If you understand, please reply.
Okay！ Then, are we going home？
Ah, can you go first？ I still have something to buy.
Ah, you still have something to buy？ Well then, I'll go with you.
It's okay, don't worry. It's just a little something I forgot.
(Umm, ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is nowhere to be seen...)
Good morning. The weather's nice today, isn't it？
Good morning. I really hope it's sunny over there too.
Hmm, according to the weather forecast, today is a good day to travel. The greens are in full bloom.
Good morning. It's going to be hot today.
You're right. Do you think it's going to be cool over there？
It's still early for the autumn leaves, but it seems to be colder in the morning and evening.
Oh, isn't that perfect for preliminary research？
Yeah. Because, you know, it's a school trip！
I see. Yeah, it's a school trip after all！
We'll be riding the limited express after this, right？
Yes, the limited express. And change trains at the Tobu Railway.
You even know the transfer schedules, as expected of you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Actually... I brought the hours as a bookmark for our trip.
I see！ It's full-scale... Did you make this, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
I did it and brought it to help us in our school trip.
Yes！ I made another one, here you go.
Oh... isn't it like the Shinkansen？
It's so cool.. A 100-type train for limited express named Spacia. This one is purple, so it's "Miyavi".
Spacia seems to go really fast. Even going as far as checking the vehicles, as expected ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Yeah, I just happen to know that.
("Happen to know". That's something I didn't knew...)
I brought it with me again.
Hmm？ Have you been subtly upgrading it？
Yes. I added a little bit of things I learned from our previous trip, photos, and so on.
If you make it this way, it'll be a memory of our trip... together.
Limited Express Spacia... Are you thrilled to see it？... ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
I wonder if I can see it...
I wondered if I could see the dolly. There is something I wanted to check.
(▲高嶺＊＊▲, maybe you... well, it's fine.)
Hmm... A large seat in a larger car！ Limited express is so good！
Hehe！ It feels like you're going on a trip, right？
That's right. Speaking of which... you brought a great baggage like always, right？
Hmm... I didn't want to leave behind something that I'd need.
Then spare clothes... and what else？
A face wash set, a brush and a shampoo, right？ And... other things.
You're right, because we're staying in an inn, right？
And that's why... I'm worried that I'm not used to it yet...
It's because... I want to look pretty, always, when we're together.
It's so nice... There is a lot of green in the view from the window.
Isn't it time to decide who is the leading sensei？
Leading sensei！？ Do you want to have one？
Because it's more like a school trip with a sensei, right？
I wonder... Then, since you do research about things, ▲高嶺＊＊▲, you're the sensei？
Hehe！ I look forward for your guidance, sensei▼
(I suppose this was decided from the beginning...)
Then, this time it's your turn to be the sensei, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
I want to call you "sensei". Isn't it good？ Sensei▼
Soon, we will arrive at Kinugawa Hot Springs. Please, make sure you don't forget anything...
We finally arrived at Kinugawa Hot Springs.
Don't you feel it was faster than expected？ Alright, it's time to get off！
We arrived to Kinugawa hot springs...
Yeah... We're staying here tonight, right？
No, when you said that, I got a little nervous...
Hehe, it's funny！ Hey, what's that？ Is it a demon？ Oh, there is also a foot-bath！ Do you want to go in？
Okay. However, let's leave our luggage in the locker at the station first... Wow, it's heavy.
We'll be under your care once more, Kinuta-san.
Can I take a picture with Kinuta-san？
When it comes to school trips, you get so excited ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Thank you. It's my fist time riding this line.
Are you nervous ▲高嶺＊＊▲？ Anyway, let's get down to the river.
I see... The flow is pretty steep on the other side.
Hey, we're going on that wooden boat, right？
Right. Oh, it looks like boarding has begun.
Yes, we're going to ride that wooden boat, right？
It'll be okay！ Takane！ It's a group activity, hurry up！
Thank you. We still have some time, do you want to head down early？
The water is clean... I feel that the air is delicious near the river.
▲高嶺＊＊▲ isn't it quite different from the first time？
It's because they were explaining about life jackets, I imagined the river was dangerous...
Sorry to keep you waiting！ Please, start boarding！
Hey, hey... It looks like there's a waterfall over there...
Look, we'll be covered with water！
Hey, did you get it？ It's a gorilla rock！
I saw it！ It's the profile of a gorilla, right？
Oh... I'm a little disappointed now...
You're right. It's also interesting to find rocks.
How many do you know？ Aside from the gorilla rock？ The elephant rock, dog rock and... the haunted rock！
That's a little less subtle, right？
Just a little, right？ Haa... the river feels so cool！
Yes, it was... Ah, hey, is that...？
Grilled sweetfish with salt？ Sounds nice, why don't we try it？
Isn't it fine to be a little wild？ We're together anyway.
Back in elementary school I couldn't help but wanting to try it.
But, sensei scolded me and I felt a little sad.
You endured so much. Okay then. Today, sensei will eat, so Takane can eat too！
Oh, it looks like the bus has come！
Alright, our next stop is Tobu World Square！
It seems that the water's flow today is a little steeper.
You think so？ Ah, look, grilled sweetfish with salt, do you want to eat？
Alright, our next stop is Tobu World Square！
This is Tobu World Square. Did you come here on a school trip in elementary school, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Huh, are you feeling sick... Ah, did you get sick on the bus？
I'm fine. I just remembered something...
I visited Tobu World Square on the second day, but the night before, the night I stayed...
Even when the light were off, everyone was making a fuss and couldn't sleep.
Isn't that fine on a school trip？
Really？ But I was sleepy all the way...
That's why I went to sensei's room to lie down. The sensei went to scold everyone.
The next day, I was all alone...
So, neither my friends nor I are in the photo I took at the time. Only the photo of the model in close-up.
This is the entrance to Tobu World Square. Customers who get off should not forget anything...
We arrived to the encounter of everyone's dreams. This is Tobu World Square...
Do you want to take a lot of pictures？ This time, you'll be in the center ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
This is the entrance to Tobu World Square. Customers who get off should not forget anything...
The encounter of everyone's dreams. Tobu World Square...
Hehe, you like that catch phrase, right？
Maybe. Let's go find the dreams and excitement！
Oh！？ Amazing... The world at a １／２５ scale.
Isn't it amazing？ The buildings are so elaborated, but if you look closely, you can see――
The little people are doing a lot of things. Did you notice？
Oh, it's really well done. Well, first of all... over there.
It's amazing... the train is moving...
Hmm, you're right～... Are you fine into looking a little more？
(The tittle is "Great Manaka, Tokyo Station Invasion！ Run People！".)
Even if you look at the skyscrapers in New York like this, it's still huge...
Yeah, even if I become a monster, I don't think I can destroy it...
Japan must work harder... Oh, I got inspired！ ▲高嶺＊＊▲, over there！
Reporters are gathering at the front door. Oh, is that the Prime Minister？
That's right. So, why don't you just shake your fist like this？
(Title, "Great Manaka, puts pressure on the Diet！".)
I don't know some of them, but many are famous！
Palace of Versailles！ Oh yeah, the garden was so nice that I took a picture...
Hey, when you take a pic with the camera close to the ground, it looks really big, right？
I see！ Then... that's it！ The Eiffel Tower！
If it's a １／２５ scale, it will be like this, right？
Oh, I like it！ Why don't you try reaching out to the tower？
With my hand？ Something like this？
Kyaa！ What？ Why taking it from there...
No, no！ It's not what you think！
Tobu World Square is so fun！ It feels like we're going around the world！
Hehe！ I also had a lot of fun.
You're so kind... I love you.
Hey, can you show me the photos？
...Huh？ Ah, the bus is here, right？ This time, we go to EDO WONDERLAND in Nikko Edomura.
I see. Then show them to me in the bus. Hehe, I'm looking forward to it！
(I hope you won't get angry when you see them, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
It's been fun！ I really feel like we've found dreams and excitement！
Hehe, but you took weird photos.
You think so？ I think they are all masterpieces, right？
Thank you... You made this my favorite place.
We've arrived at EDO WONDERLAND in Nikko Edomura. Passengers should make sure they don't forget anything...
From here, we can't really feel the wonderland.
You're a little strict, look... it's like a checkpoint.
Yes. Um, do you give the ticket to someone like a gatekeeper？
Customer, do you have a bill of passage？
Yes？ Um... Eh？ Bill of passage？
Ah, yes！ Here are two adult tickets, um... Gozaru.
▲高嶺＊＊▲... Did you really said that？
I would have felt bad if I didn't...
We arrived at EDO WONDERLAND in Nikko Edomura. Passengers should make sure they don't forget anything...
EDO WONDERLAND... we arrived once more.
Hmm... You bought the tickets, right？
Our bills of passage, you mean.
Hmm, is that right？ Bill of passage？
Yes. Some are like sets, but there are also real shops, right？
The people walking here are all Edo tradesmen. It's really elaborate...
This is more than I expected...
... Hehe！ Haha！ Hahaha！ This is so funny！
Because, Hehe！ Hey！ Let's go to other places！
▲高嶺＊＊▲, this seems like a slapstick...
It smells good... Oh, yakitori. And soba and Kamamesi Matsumaeya.
Speaking of which, it's already past noon... ▲高嶺＊＊▲, are you hungry？
(Geez, what kind of character is that...)
Hey, did you see the menu？ It says "Curry Udon". Hehe！
Ah, really. Umm, Shogun Kamamesi... １，８００ gold coins！？ Let's just have "Curry Udon".
Then I want... Hmm, herbs Kamamesi！
That procession is... the "Crow Ninja Mansion", huh.
"Crow Ninja Mansion"！ I want to go！
It's amazing. Even if you know that there is a mechanism, you'll be fooled... Kyaa！
I was surprised... The face of a ninja was in front of me...
Hmm... isn't that a little too close？
I don't want anyone else to see how cute you are, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
No way, I just happen to be a normal girl.
(I don't think that's the case ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Ah, look！ Look at that！ It's "Ninja Kaikai-tei"！
I like those kinds of ninja things... Then, let's enter――
So-somehow, I have a sense of balance...
What？ Why？ Ah, this is funny！！
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！ It's dangerous to run！
Watch out！ That's why I told you――
(Huh？ We're alone, this kind of development...)
(Rather than being a ninja, I like this kind of thing...)
The journey of Oiran begins. Please, take a look at the Oiran's elegant "Oneri"！
I wonder what it feels like to gather longing eyes on you, and parade around like that...
▲高嶺＊＊▲, would you like to try it too？
It's impossible！ I'm sure I'll be nervous... But...
After all, don't girls yearn for it？
I prefer to do it alone.
Because if you don't really like it, then...
(Okay, the souvenir shops are over there... Huh, where is ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
Sorry to keep you waiting. Hey, look at this？
It has our names in each of them. So... "Manaka" is yours, then...
Yeah... to commemorate today... can you carry it with you？
Likewise... Thank you for accepting it...
I'm feeling a little shy, don't you？ The bus is here, let's go！ Our next stop is finally the inn！
Yeah！ Huh... what did you mean with "finally"？
(It didn't have a that kind of meaning...)
▲高嶺＊＊▲, aren't you always super happy when we come here？
Certainly. EDO WONDERLAND is like that, right？ Isn't the bus coming soon？
Yes, we're finally staying at the inn, right？
Look, don't you want to "have a pillow fight" once again！？
Ah！ Oh, over there！ What is that...
Huh... what are you talking about？
Now that you mention it, I'm starving！
Now then, the bus to Kinugawa Plaza Hotel is...
Sorry to keep you waiting, guests staying at Kinugawa Plaza Hotel！
And we arrived！ This is our inn for today, Kinugawa Plaza Hotel！
Such a grand hotel... And a big... Ball？
Sorry to keep you waiting. I was checking in. Supper is at 7 o'clock.
Thank you. Hey... we're really here, right？ It's pretty good, but...
I think there is no doubt...
Sorry to keep you waiting. We will guide you to your room. Want someone to carry your wife's luggage？
Eh！？ Ah, well, we are on a school trip――
Sorry to keep you waiting, guests staying at Kinugawa Plaza Hotel！
And we arrived！ This is Kinugawa Plaza Hotel！
The big ball！ And the treasured hot springs！
Sorry to keep you waiting. I was checking in. Supper is at 7 o'clock.
Thank you. It's so wide inside... like a museum...
Yes, the first time, I was a little impatient...
Sorry to keep you waiting. We will guide you to your room. Want someone to carry your wife's luggage？
Eh！？ Ah, yes！ Um, I'm fine！
Now then, please take your time and relax.
Ah, it's a nice room... There's even a dining room... Oh, look outside！
There's an open-air bath... You can take a bath while looking down on the Kinugawa river...
Ah, no... I just said it.
Geez... It seems a little too luxurious for a school trip room...
It's a nice room... You can even see Kinugawa really well.
The furniture is cool and it looks like a luxury condominium, right？
Really, it has a small sink. I wonder if it's a condominium, rather than a school trip...
...I won't say it. Even though you know it, you're just being mean...
(What were you imagining？ Don't be shy...)
Do you want to go to the public baths before dinner？
Ah, agreed！ Do you want to go now？
Well then, I'll meet you here after bath. If I'm late, forgive me okay？
Girls always take too much time！ I'll drink something while I wait.
Good luck with the "Treasure hot springs"！
It's so wide～！ And it's overlooking the Kinugawa river！ It feels so good～！
(Haa～, my body is getting rid of today's stress... I'm getting sleepy...)
Alright, it's time to get up！
This is dangerous... I have to really get up...
Umm, and I think ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is...
This is good after all... A nice hot spring trip.
The hot water was so good, wasn't it？
Hehe, you took a long bath, didn't you？
Excuse me. I'm here to prepare your meal.
Hehe！ Even though it's a school trip, is this okay？
Being in a room like this, taking a break, like a date――
I can't eat everything, so please eat the meat.
Now that we're not hungry, would you like to explore inside the hotel？
There are some things I wanna see. Specialties such as Utsunomiya dumplings and local sweets...
▲主人公＊▲. Did you find something good？
Well, there are a lot to chose from, right？ How about there？
Hey, want to play a little？
As a tennis club member, I have to do it！
Here I come... ▲高嶺＊＊▲, don't take it too seriously.
You call it table tennis, right？ I just got serious about it. Hehe♪
You have to raise your arms even more, even though you're wearing a yukata, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Let's go back to the room！
I'm completely sweaty... I wonder if I'll have to take a bath again.
Oh, then why don't we take the "spa" this time？ It's a private bath, you know...
Like a hot spring with spa！ Maybe...
Ah, look, isn't it over there？
It's really nice... Hey, shall we go？
Hehe, it's like a bath in the forest, right？
It's not like a school trip, though！
Then, let's take a break until we have to go back to the room.
Okay, let me wash your back, I'm kidding♪
Is it time to go out？
Hmm. Then... want to go out first？ I still want to relax a little more.
Ah, remember that you can't take long baths, okay？
Hmm, but... I can't wear a yukata with a wet swimsuit...
We arrived at Kinugawa. We will take a little break here from our school trip, right？
There's a lot of people here！ I wonder if they are high school students too！
Right, Hehe. Sit down and stretch your back a while♪
I'm not hesitating, because... Geez, okay！ Sit down, please.
▲主人公＊▲. Sorry to keep you waiting.
The hot water was good, wasn't it？ Haa...
(Hmm！ Her yukata looks so sexy after all...)
Geez, what is it？ Don't look at me that much...
Huh？ Oh, I was just thinking your yukata looks good.
Ah, I-I see... But, you look good too.
Yes... you look great. Manly and nice.
We're still taking a break, even though we're pretending to be on a school trip...
Hey, can I buy a drink somewhere？
A drink？ Then, surely in the refrigerator――
Then, if I went to buy it, would you come to look for me later？
She's not here... where did you go？
She's not here either... Where is she？ ▲高嶺＊＊▲, where...
How far have you gone？ Hey, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Mustn't you say instead "You're past bedtime！", sensei？
Well then... Hey！ You're past your bedtime！
I'm sorry！ I'll head back soon！
Now then, it's a little early to go to bed―― What should we do, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Hehe, we're having a pillow fight♪
I see, it's something you do on a school trip, right？ But, wasn't I the sensei？
And that's why... What should we do before going to bed...
Hmm... have you decided which one do you want？
No, even if I was told to decide...
I want you to decide. What I'm saying is...
Ah, I see. But... What do you want to do ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Ah, you also liked the one by the wall, right？ Then, I――
No, no... It's alright, okay？ ▲高嶺＊＊▲, you can have the bed by the wall.
(It was a little confusing... I was so surprised...)
Hehe, me too. Then, shall we turn off the lights？
There is one more thing I wanted to do, since we're on a school trip.
What do you want to do？
Would you like to confess who you like？
My favorite person... has a wonderful laugh and a nice smile,
Actually, he's a man, and tells me a lot of things I don't know...
(Somehow, I feel like it's not me...)
He's a little pervert, but he's very kind...
He's my doubles partner in the tennis club... I won't tell you any more.
Hmm... Well, the person I like...
Haa～～！ It's time to go to bed！
Before that, don't we have something to do？ You know, speaking of school trips...
Hehe, want to enter the futon？
The person I like... that's right...
Okay, a hint. Is it from the same club？
Now then, is it from the same class？
Yes～, if I say that, I'll get caught.
Don't be mean, tell me please？
Then, what is Ｍ・Ｔ good at？
Study, sports？ It's the ace of the tennis club, and she's so cute！
Really... Then how much do you like her？
(I'm glad I got up early, because I slept properly yesterday！)
Did you sleep well～？ It's a shame, but it's morning already, okayー？
If you don't wake up... I'll pinch your nose！ Hehe！
You're still sleeping... So cute▼ Then, take this！
Huh？ ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s not here... What happened？
Is she in the bathroom？ ▲高嶺＊＊▲ー？ Are you there？
Eh！？ No, don't come over here！
Because breakfast is ready. Hey, hurry up and change your clothes, okay？
Wow, you can really see Kinugawa！ There seems to be a terrace seat there.
Both Japanese and Western foods are available to order！
Really！ Freshly baked bread. Japanese food from this area is "Obanzai"！
Sorry to make you wait. Maybe I took too much food♪
It's true, I took a lot too！
There are a lot of pickles that look delicious... Ah, you took some too.
Hehe, today we have to go to Nikko, right？ We have to eat a lot, and do our best！
Thank you. We look forward to seeing you again.
Alright, now... ▲高嶺＊＊▲, sorry to keep you waiting！
"Kinugawa Plaza Hotel" was such a good hotel！
Yeah... We made a lot of good memories. I hope we can come again.
I wish I could win the prize again... I know, do you want to take a photo to commemorate this？
Good！ Then, we head for Nikko today！
Hurry up！ The train will leave！
Haa, haa... This makes a transfer somewhere？
Yes！ If we can't get on the next one, we'll have to wait a long time！
(I knew it, you should be the sensei, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
I'm glad we made it in time. ▲高嶺＊＊▲, your "Traveling Bookmark" is perfect, isn't it？
Thank you... Oh, it's a two-car train.
It will be expanded at Shimoimaichi Station. At Tobu Nikko, the first two cars will be organized.
It was written in the bookmark, right？ Hehe▼
(I wonder if it really was there...)
Now we change trains at Shimoimaichi and we head to Tobu Nikko station, right？
Thank you for all your help, Kinuta-san. See you later.
Yes, a 2-car formation. Hehe！ Let's get the seats in the back, so we can easily see Mt. Nantai.
(I knew it, you should be in the role of sensei, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Yes, Mt. Nantai！ It looks so close...
It seems to be higher than I expected. I think the altitude is in the "bookmark"――
Mt. Nantai, also know as Nikko Fuji, was revised in 2003 as 2,486m. Even from Nikko, it's over 1,200m.
Discovered by Shodo Shonin in 782, and is also the Shrine for the deity of Futarasan. Did I do well, sensei？
Yes！ Don't you feel like the air here is a little colder than Kinugawa？
Maybe？ Ah, the bus stop is――.
Before that, let's leave our luggage in the locker.
I see！ As expected from Takane's tours！
Ah, I can see Mt. Nantai.
Yes. What kind of face will you show today, I wonder...
Don't you sound like a poet？
We arrived！ Now then, let's leave our luggage and go to the bus... Ah, are you okay with the bus？
I'll be fine. I took medicine to prevent sickness, and――
Also, you'll help me look for Irowa？
Going to Irohazaka by bus... Does that make you nervous？
I'm fine. Are you looking forward to Irohazaka？
Oh... As expected from "Irohazaka". It's a sight to behold...
Okay, then read the letters on the sign by the curve！
Ah！ Then you saw everything from the beginning, ▲高嶺＊＊▲
The smell of colors in my world. It's a significant Okuyama, beyond that it's a shallow dream today.
Hehe, geez！ Oh, look！ Huh, isn't that "ka"？
Umm... Ah, there it is！ I want to start from there.
I see, after getting off the elevator we can begin.
That's right, because this is on the waterfall. Shall we go？
See, you can already hear it！！
We made it to Nikko, both of us, together...
Kegon Falls, one of Japan's three famous waterfalls, flows out of Lake Chuzenji, it goes 97m―― Ah, look！
Truly, this is a great view...
I'm sorry, umm, it's drop is 97m to the bottom, and――
It's fine, let's enjoy the view.
Haa... When you come here, you realize it, right？
Hey, have you noticed that there are many wonderful things around Kegon Falls？
The sound of a small waterfall around？
That is one of the Twelve Waterfalls. You can see the waterfall at the bottom, right？ And...
Look over there！ Did you see it？
Huh？ That rock like a pillar？
